com.amplifyframework.api.aws

Class SelectionSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amplifyframework.api.aws.SelectionSet

  • public final class SelectionSet
extends java.lang.Object
    Class representing a node of a SelectionSet for use in a GraphQLDocument. A root SelectionSet node will have a null value.
